room_title: Escape room "Captain's Quarters" by Escape NE Ohio in Warren
room_address: 200 Chestnut Avenue Northeast Suite C Warren, OH 44483
room_description: The year is 1718, treasure hunters near and far have been searching for the wreckage of Blackbeard's infamous flagship Queen Anne's Revenge. Blackbeard, even in death, watches over his prize with his cursing gaze. Legend states that the only time the diamond can be taken without suffering the wrath of Blackbeard's curse is to find it today, during the 60 minutes when the Blood Moon sits at its apex.
